You can exchange the UK digital copy codes for US codes. Just go to sonypicturesstore dot com slash help dot html and chat, call or e-mail. They will validate your UK codes and provide you with US codes, it was very simple. Oh and the movies are pretty great.

Great deal for both movies! As it was previously stated that the digital copy codes don't work in the US. But, this can be resolved by emailing Sony Pictures store. Just do a Google search for "Sony Pictures digital copy" and that should point you in the right direction. I received replacement codes from them so now I have the digital copies.

These movies are funny, and the price I paid for both is worth it. Both have great jokes, which sometimes the sequel falls flat on jokes in movies, but this franchise had me laughing in both movies.

I didn't read carefully and wasn't aware that my codes wouldn't work in the US. I called Sony to see if I could do anything about it and their customer service is AMAZING. She was able to add both digital movies to my Vudu account! Emailing won't get you a response, but it took all of 5 minutes tops to call and have the Digital Copies added!
